name: Daisy Coin 2.0
description: Daisy coin was created using epoxy resin,alcohol ink,and fresh pressed flowers. With a deep appreciation and love for flower preservation, I created a coin inspired by my enthusiastic outlook on the future of crypto currencies. The gears are symbolic for the ending of an era and the changing times that are inevitable. Daisy Coin 1.0 was the first NFT minted on the blockchain by artist Flower P0wer https://opensea.io/assets 0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/840837291191973515562778370724
